### Get all orders
GET {{url}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all orders for client
GET {{url}}/orders?clientId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get order by ID
GET {{url}}/orders/4
Content-Type: application/json

### Get sales history
GET {{url}}/orders/sales?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2026-01-31
Content-Type: application/json

### Create new order
POST {{url}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "client": {
    "id": 1
